# Project Structure

Single Next.js 14 portfolio website (no monorepo, no backend API).

```
src/
  app/
    page.tsx          → Homepage (card-grid layout)
    blog/page.tsx     → Blog index
    blog/[slug]/      → Blog post pages (MDX)
    build-mvp/        → MVP request board (Canny-style)
    robots.ts         → Generated robots.txt
    sitemap.ts        → Generated sitemap.xml
  components/
    layout/           → SiteHeader (with mobile hamburger menu)
    ui/               → shadcn/ui primitives (button, input, textarea, card-shell)
    JsonLd.tsx        → Reusable JSON-LD structured data component
  lib/
    blog.ts           → MDX blog post reader (gray-matter + next-mdx-remote)
    design.ts         → Design token loader from design.json
    utils.ts          → Tailwind merge utility
content/
  blog/               → MDX blog post files (frontmatter: title, description, date, tags)
design.json           → Source-of-truth design system tokens
public/               → Static assets (profile.jpg, portfolio images)
.agents/skills/       → Marketing skills (coreyhaines31/marketingskills)
```

## Key Conventions

- **No backend / no API** — this is a static portfolio site
- **Design tokens** live in `design.json` and are exposed as CSS variables in `globals.css`
- **Styling** uses `var(--*)` CSS variables inline (e.g. `bg-[var(--card)]`, `text-[var(--text)]`)
- **Dark theme only** — background `#0B0F19`, accent `#8B5CF6`
- **SEO**: JSON-LD structured data, per-page metadata, robots.txt, sitemap.xml
- **Blog**: MDX files in `content/blog/`, parsed by `src/lib/blog.ts`
- Path alias `@/` maps to `./src/`

## Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `npm run dev` | Start dev server on port 3000 |
| `npm run build` | Production build |
| `npm run lint` | ESLint check |
| `npm run clean` | Remove .next and node_modules |
